| Priority | Item | Impact | Effort |
|---|---|---|---|
| **P0** | Real ECRECOVER (libsecp256k1) | Unlocks all DeFi | 1-2 days |
| **P0** | Transient Storage (TLOAD/TSTORE) | Unlocks re-entrancy guards, flash loans | 2-3 days |
| **P0** | CREATE2 syscall | Unlocks factory patterns, DEXs | 1-2 days |
| **P1** | Turbine shredding activation | Network layer for 1M TPS | 3-5 days |
| **P1** | Async state root hashing | Unblocks execution pipeline | 3-5 days |
| **P1** | Memory prefetching in DAG scheduler | Eliminates L3 cache misses | 2-3 days |
| **P2** | AOT/JIT compilation | 15x VM speedup | 2-4 weeks |
| **P2** | io_uring for ZephyrDB | Eliminates kernel I/O overhead | 1 week |
| **P2** | Lock-free delta merge | Eliminates merge contention | 1 week |
| **P3** | BLS12-381 precompiles | ZK proof verification | 1-2 weeks |
| **P3** | Source mapping / debug tooling | Developer experience | 1-2 weeks |
| **P3** | Gas estimation RPC | Standard UX | 2-3 days |

